title: Honey apple cake
ingredients: ['150g butter or margarine, softened', '165g light brown soft sugar', '3 eggs', '180ml honey', '2 teaspoons lemon zest', '120ml strong freshly brewed coffee', '250g plain flour', '180g wholemeal wheat flour', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1/4 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '3/4 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '250g apples, peeled, cored and diced', '60g walnuts, coarsely chopped']
